author: AdrianoDee
body:
#### PR description:

Adding `D95` (latest baseline) to Patatrack wfs. Keeping `D88` for a smoother transition. Will remove it later. The new wfs will inherit then the numbering `23634.*` and `23834.*` (no PU, PU). Adding also the various `FullRecoGPU` wfs for Phase2 (e.g. `.582`, `.592`, ...).

#### PR validation:

None. Technical PR. Testing the new wfs.
title: Adding D95 Patatack wfs and the FullRecoGPU wfs for Phase2
